---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Aktivizace seniorů – canisterapie, muzikoterapie, ergoterapie | Domov Turovice"
  description="Aktivizace seniorů v Domově Turovice: canisterapie s border kolií Kirou, muzikoterapie s harmonikářem Ivanem, ergoterapie každý všední den, trénink paměti, rehabilitace a duchovní péče."
>

<style>
/* ── HERO ── */
.akt-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--clr-primary) 0%, #7a3238 100%);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 80px 0 64px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.akt-hero::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  right: -80px; top: -80px;
  width: 420px; height: 420px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.akt-hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 700px; }
.akt-hero .section-label-sm { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); }
.akt-hero h1 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff;
  margin: 0 0 18px;
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.akt-hero-perex {
  font-size: var(--font-size-perex);
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.88);
  margin: 0;
  max-width: 580px;
}
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .akt-hero { padding: 56px 0 44px; }
}



/* ── SHARED SECTION LABEL ── */
.section-label-sm {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-label);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

/* ── INTRO – dvousloupcový ── */
.intro-section { background: var(--clr-bg); padding: 88px 0; }
.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 64px;
  align-items: center;
}
.about-text h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.about-text p {
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--clr-text);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.benefit-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; margin-top: 24px; }
.benefit-list li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 12px;
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--clr-text);
}
.benefit-check {
  width: 22px; height: 22px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--clr-green-soft);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;
}
.benefit-check svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; stroke: var(--clr-green); fill: none; stroke-width: 2.5; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
.about-visual {
  background: var(--clr-green-soft);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 44px 40px;
  text-align: center;
}
.av-number {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 64px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-green);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.av-label {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-label);
  color: var(--clr-green);
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.av-divider { width: 40px; height: 2px; background: var(--clr-green); margin: 0 auto 28px; }
.av-quote {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: var(--font-size-subhead);
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.av-quote-author {
  margin-top: 14px;
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  color: var(--clr-muted);
  font-weight: 600;
}
@media (max-width: 1024px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; } }

/* ── PROGRAMY ── */
.programs-section { background: var(--clr-surface); padding: 88px 0; }
.section-intro { text-align: center; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto 52px; }
.section-intro h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.section-intro p { font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: 1.65; color: var(--clr-text); }

.programs-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
}
.prog-card {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  overflow: hidden;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  transition: box-shadow .25s, transform .25s;
}
.prog-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover); transform: translateY(-4px); }
.prog-card-accent { height: 4px; background: var(--clr-green); }
.prog-card-accent.orange { background: var(--clr-orange); }
.prog-card-accent.blue   { background: var(--clr-blue); }
.prog-card-accent.primary { background: var(--clr-primary); }
.prog-card-body { padding: 28px; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

.prog-icon {
  width: 46px; height: 46px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background: var(--clr-green-soft);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.prog-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; stroke: var(--clr-green); fill: none; stroke-width: 2; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
.prog-icon.orange { background: var(--clr-orange-soft); }
.prog-icon.orange svg { stroke: var(--clr-orange); }
.prog-icon.blue { background: var(--clr-blue-soft); }
.prog-icon.blue svg { stroke: var(--clr-blue); }
.prog-icon.primary { background: var(--clr-primary-soft); }
.prog-icon.primary svg { stroke: var(--clr-primary); }

.prog-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: var(--font-size-h3);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.prog-card-meta { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.prog-tag {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-label);
  font-weight: 700;
  background: var(--clr-green-soft);
  color: var(--clr-green);
}
.prog-tag svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 2; flex-shrink: 0; }
.prog-tag.orange { background: var(--clr-orange-soft); color: var(--clr-orange); }
.prog-tag.blue   { background: var(--clr-blue-soft);   color: var(--clr-blue);   }
.prog-tag.primary { background: var(--clr-primary-soft); color: var(--clr-primary); }

.prog-card p { font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: 1.7; color: var(--clr-text); flex: 1; }
.prog-card-who {
  margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 14px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  color: var(--clr-muted);
}
.prog-card-who strong { color: var(--clr-heading); font-weight: 600; }

@media (max-width: 1024px) { .programs-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 600px)  { .programs-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* ── REHABILITACE ── */
.rehab-section { background: #fff; padding: 88px 0; }
.rehab-box {
  background: var(--clr-orange-soft);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 52px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 52px;
  align-items: center;
}
.rehab-icon-big {
  width: 68px; height: 68px;
  border-radius: 18px;
  background: rgba(200,144,42,0.15);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.rehab-icon-big svg { width: 34px; height: 34px; stroke: var(--clr-orange); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.8; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
.rehab-box h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.rehab-box p { font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: 1.75; color: var(--clr-text); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.rehab-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; margin-top: 8px; }
.rehab-list li {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  color: var(--clr-text);
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.rehab-list li::before {
  content: '';
  width: 8px; height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--clr-orange);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 7px;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) { .rehab-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; padding: 32px 24px; } }

/* ── DUCHOVNÍ PÉČE ── */
.spirit-section { background: var(--clr-bg); padding: 88px 0; }
.spirit-card {
  background: var(--clr-primary-soft);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 48px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 36px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.spirit-icon {
  width: 60px; height: 60px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  background: rgba(155,66,73,0.12);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.spirit-icon svg { width: 28px; height: 28px; stroke: var(--clr-primary); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.8; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
.spirit-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: var(--font-size-h3);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.spirit-card p { font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: 1.75; color: var(--clr-text); margin-bottom: 14px; }
.spirit-card p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .spirit-card { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; padding: 28px 24px; } }

/* ── PÉČE O SEBE ── */
.pece-section { background: var(--clr-surface); padding: 88px 0; }
.pece-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
  margin-top: 0;
}
.pece-item {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  padding: 28px 24px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}
.pece-item-icon {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background: var(--clr-blue-soft);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}
.pece-item-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; stroke: var(--clr-blue); fill: none; stroke-width: 2; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
.pece-item h4 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: var(--font-size-h4);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
}
.pece-item p { font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: 1.65; color: var(--clr-text); margin: 0; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .pece-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* ── AKCE ── */
.events-section { background: #fff; padding: 88px 0; }
.events-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
}
.event-card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--clr-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  padding: 28px 24px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  transition: box-shadow .2s, border-color .2s;
}
.event-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover); border-color: var(--clr-primary); }
.event-emoji {
  width: 50px; height: 50px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: var(--clr-green-soft);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 22px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.event-card h4 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: var(--font-size-h4);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.event-card p { font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: 1.65; color: var(--clr-text); margin: 0; }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .events-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* ── CTA ── */
.cta-section {
  background: #EDE8E3;
  padding: 88px 0;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.cta-section::before { content: ''; position: absolute; width: 360px; height: 360px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(155,66,73,0.08); top: -80px; right: -80px; pointer-events: none; }
.cta-section::after  { content: ''; position: absolute; width: 220px; height: 220px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(155,66,73,0.05); bottom: -60px; left: -60px; pointer-events: none; }
.cta-inner { text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.cta-inner h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3.5vw, 2.3rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.cta-inner p { font-size: var(--font-size-perex); line-height: 1.65; color: var(--clr-text-body); margin-bottom: 32px; }
.cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.cta-group .btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 13px 24px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: var(--font-size-ui);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all .2s;
}
.btn-primary { background: var(--clr-primary); color: #fff; border: 2px solid var(--clr-primary); }
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--clr-primary-hover); border-color: var(--clr-primary-hover); }
.btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--clr-primary); border: 2px solid var(--clr-primary); }
.btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--clr-primary); color: #fff; }

/* ── RELATED ── */
.related-d-section { background: var(--clr-surface); padding: 72px 0; }
.related-d-section h2 { font-family: var(--ff-head); font-size: var(--font-size-h2); font-weight: 700; color: var(--clr-primary); margin: 0 0 8px; }
.related-d-label { font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-label); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--clr-primary); display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.related-d-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 36px; }
.related-d-card { background: #fff; border-radius: var(--radius-card); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); padding: 28px 24px; text-decoration: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; border-top: 3px solid var(--clr-border); transition: box-shadow .22s, transform .22s, border-top-color .22s; color: inherit; }
.related-d-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover); transform: translateY(-4px); border-top-color: var(--clr-primary); }
.related-d-card-label { font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-label); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .07em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--clr-muted); }
.related-d-card-title { font-family: var(--ff-head); font-size: var(--font-size-subhead); font-weight: 600; color: var(--clr-text-dark); line-height: 1.35; }
.related-d-card-desc { font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-base); color: var(--clr-muted); line-height: 1.55; flex: 1; }
.related-d-card-arrow { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-caption); font-weight: 600; color: var(--clr-primary); margin-top: 4px; transition: gap .18s; }
.related-d-card:hover .related-d-card-arrow { gap: 10px; }
.related-d-card-arrow svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 2; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
@media (max-width: 1024px) { .related-d-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 768px)  { .related-d-section { padding: 56px 0; } .related-d-section h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-h2-mob); } }
@media (max-width: 480px)  { .related-d-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>

<!-- ══ HERO ══ -->
<header class="akt-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="akt-hero-inner">
      <span class="section-label-sm">Péče a služby</span>
      <h1>Aktivizace seniorů v Domově Turovice</h1>
      <p class="akt-hero-perex">Canisterapie, muzikoterapie, ergoterapie i trénink paměti. Každý den u nás něco živého probíhá – proto tu klienti mají důvod ráno vstát.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>


<!-- ══ INTRO ══ -->
<section class="intro-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <span class="section-label-sm">Proč nám na aktivizaci záleží</span>
        <h2>Aktivní den je dobrý den</h2>
        <p>Aktivizace není jen vyplnění volného času. Je to způsob, jak udržovat mozek čilý, ruce v pohybu a srdce otevřené. U seniorů se sníženou soběstačností má pravidelná stimulace přímý dopad na kvalitu života, náladu i zdravotní stav.</p>
        <p>V Domově Turovice nabízíme pestrý program každý všední den. Nezáleží na tom, jak je klient pohyblivý – máme aktivity pro skupiny i pro ty, kdo tráví den na pokoji.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>
            <span class="benefit-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>
            <span>Program přizpůsobený individuálním schopnostem každého klienta</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="benefit-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>
            <span>Aktivity skupinové i individuální – nikdo není vynechaný</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="benefit-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>
            <span>Propojení fyzické, kognitivní i emocionální složky pohody</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="benefit-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>
            <span>Certifikovaný trénink paměti vedený zkušenými pracovnicemi</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="about-visual">
        <div class="av-number">104</div>
        <div class="av-label">klientů v péči</div>
        <div class="av-divider"></div>
        <p class="av-quote">„Aktivní senior je spokojený senior. Každý den hledáme cesty, jak probudit radost z tvoření i pohybu."</p>
        <p class="av-quote-author">Aktivizační tým Domova Turovice</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ PROGRAMY ══ -->
<section class="programs-section" id="programy">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-intro">
      <span class="section-label-sm">Co u nás probíhá</span>
      <h2>Naše aktivizační programy</h2>
      <p>Každý program má svůj rytmus, svého průvodce a svůj účel. Podívejte se, co u nás každý týden probíhá.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="programs-grid">

      <article class="prog-card">
        <div class="prog-card-accent"></div>
        <div class="prog-card-body">
          <div class="prog-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="9" cy="12" r="2"/><path d="M4 12c0-3.314 2.686-6 6-6s6 2.686 6 6-2.686 6-6 6"/><path d="M14 12c0-2.206 1.794-4 4-4v8c-2.206 0-4-1.794-4-4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Canisterapie</h3>
          <div class="prog-card-meta">
            <span class="prog-tag"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>1× měsíčně</span>
            <span class="prog-tag">Skupinová</span>
          </div>
          <p>Border kolie Kira navštěvuje klienty spolu se svou cvičitelkou Nikolou Petříkovou z Přerova. Dotek srsti, přítomnost zvířete a klidný kontakt dělají s náladou klientů zázraky – zvláště u těch, kdo celý život psy milovali.</p>
          <div class="prog-card-who"><strong>Vede:</strong> Nikola Petříková, Přerov &nbsp;·&nbsp; <strong>Pes:</strong> Kira (border kolie)</div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="prog-card">
        <div class="prog-card-accent orange"></div>
        <div class="prog-card-body">
          <div class="prog-icon orange">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Muzikoterapie</h3>
          <div class="prog-card-meta">
